original_title: Leslie Sansone: WATP Multi-Mile Mega Walk
overview: In this two-workout DVD, Leslie guides you through two complete walking workouts that blast fat and sculpt muscles. Leslie's  workouts and her encouragement will help boost energy, your attitude and your confidence.
tagline: Walk away stress and the pounds with a daily walk!
title: Leslie Sansone: WATP Multi-Mile Mega Walk
